SETLEVEL_HELP_DESCRIPTION: Set a member's level or level for member's who have a specific role.
SETLEVEL_HELP_USAGE: Set member to a specified level.```/setlevel user <member> <level>```
Update level for all member who have a specific role.```/setlevel role <member> <level>```
SETLEVEL_INCORRECT: Make sure the level you are giving is between 0 and 100.
SETLEVEL_SUCCESS: Member %s level has been set to `%s`.
SETLEVEL_NO_BOT: Unable to set the level of a bot user.
SETLEVEL_ROLE_SUCCESS: Levels have been updated for %s members.
